    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"cursed-existence\">Cursed Existence</h3><p>The Fujou are a clan of shamans and mediums that use their psychic ability to inflict curses upon their enemies. They have the special ability to peer into the world of spirits, becoming able to see what others cannot see, but the use of this ability comes at the cost of blindness to the rest of the world.</p><h4 id=\"fujou-traits\">Fujou Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increase</strong>: +2 Wis, +1 Con.<br /><strong>Speed</strong>: Your base walking speed is 30 feet.<br /><strong>Skill Proficiencies</strong>: Perception, Chakra Control<br /><strong>Cursed Technique</strong>: You know 1 additional Fujou Clan D-Rank Genjutsu</p>",
